    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Nationality, culture, or style of the Lucani, a branch of the Sabelline race that inhabited ancient Lucania, which is coextensive with the modern Italian region of Basilicata. For the culture of the city of Lucca, use "Lucchese."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
